0. Ubuntu16.04 x64

1. Install package 

sudo apt-get -y install openjdk-8-jdk git-core gnupg flex bison gperf build-essential zip curl zlib1g-dev libc6-dev-i386 lib32ncurses5-dev x11proto-core-dev libx11-dev lib32z-dev ccache libgl1-mesa-dev libxml2-utils xsltproc unzip lib32z1-dev qemu g++-multilib gcc-multilib libglib2.0-dev libpixman-1-dev linux-libc-dev:i386
sudo apt-get -y install gcc-5-aarch64-linux-gnu g++-5-aarch64-linux-gnu


2. Prepare env

export MAPLE_ROOT=/4T/proj/huawei/OpenArkCompiler
export GN_C_COMPILER=${MAPLE_ROOT}/tools/clang_llvm-8.0.0-x86_64-linux-gnu-ubuntu-16.04/bin/clang
export GN_CXX_COMPILER=${MAPLE_ROOT}/tools/clang_llvm-8.0.0-x86_64-linux-gnu-ubuntu-16.04/bin/clang++
export GN_AR_COMPILER=${MAPLE_ROOT}/tools/clang_llvm-8.0.0-x86_64-linux-gnu-ubuntu-16.04/bin/llvm-ar
export GN=${MAPLE_ROOT}/tools/gn/gn
export NINJA=${MAPLE_ROOT}/tools/ninja_1.9.0/ninja
export MAPLE_BUILD_CORE={MAPLE_ROOT}/build/core

Please update MAPLE_ROOT according to your workspace

3. Get tools
git clone https://code.opensource.huaweicloud.com/HarmonyOS/OpenArkCompiler.git
git clone https://github.com/xuyaozhong/OpenArkCompiler-tools.git

copy OpenArkCompiler-tools/tools into OpenArkCompiler workspace.

e.g.
OpenArkCompiler$ ls tools/
clang_llvm-8.0.0-x86_64-linux-gnu-ubuntu-16.04  gn  ninja_1.9.0  README



